{
  "stem": "18102.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They lived nearby, and Esther took me in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was my age.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She-- we started first grade together, and we became inseparable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If it wasn't for her, I don't know how I would have existed, because I was fairly shy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, I was more comfortable among adults than I was among children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I hadn't had that much with children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was-- I lived a lot, in my mind, alone, a lot of this period of time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And adults were normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Children weren't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she took me in, and it was truly my first girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we spent all our time in school and after school together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the premises had a inner courtyard where many of the buildings opened up into so that the courtyard became a haven for children to play games, to walk around, to sit and talk, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that courtyard I learned all the facts of life and everything that you would think-- you could think of that kids talk about or, or learn because there were many ages in that courtyard.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were kids-- five-year-olds and four-year-olds, as well as 16- and 17-year-olds-- mingling together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so you get to pick up everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think I really became quite an adult-- even though I was only eight years old-- in that courtyard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But life was fairly normal for the next-- normal in the sense that we were no longer being plagued by-- or there wasn't that fear factor around.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nobody bombing you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- and my parents got jobs as teachers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in this respect I was normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It lasted for about six months.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
